Got it.

18
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,000
(Suguro Hanji) Hey hey, it's in the opposite direction! Change course at the next intersection!

19
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,000
chef! roger that!

20
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:30,000
♬〜

21
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:33,000
Sigh…. (Mio Amao) Sigh….

22
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,000
