51
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Huh?

52
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:34,000
<This story is about seven unique detectives.>

53
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:39,000
This is a drama about a moving investigation headquarters vehicle, commonly known as Ichibanboshi, that solves cases.

54
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:52,000
(Police car siren)

55
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:55,000
This video is on Manager Akase's smartphone.

56
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,000
🖥️(Nanae) Huh!? Ah, ah….

57
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,000
Nanae….

58
