(Mio) Analyzing the voice. It has been processed and cannot be profiled by AI.

84
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,000
Huh?

85
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:38,000
🔊(Radio) Dear police vehicles, stop tracking! Stop tracking!

86
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:48,000
(Police car siren)

87
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:51,000
Bud: Is there a suspicious person on the road?

88
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,000
I don't understand!

89
00:05:57,000 --> 00:06:00,000
I mean, this truck stands out too much!

90
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,000
This is what the criminal wanted!

91
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,000
That's probably why he was nominated.

92
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,000
Destination coming soon!

93
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:14,000
(Mobile phone ringtone)

94
