97
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:25,000
This time, head towards the south exit of Shiohara Station from Shimakaze Street.

98
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,000
📞(Voice changer's voice) It's open until 5pm.

99
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,000
(slapping sound)

100
