It's close.

108
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,000
Chef Slow down! I know, I know!

109
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,000
Wow….

110
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
(Swan) Ah... Wow...

