146
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,000
Huh?

147
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,000
This car is 2.5 meters. You cannot pass! I'll take a detour!

148
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
No, I won't make it in time. I have to go...!

149
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
What is impossible is impossible! chef!

150
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:40,000
Shit...! It's a loss...

151
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,000
ᗕ(Klaxon)

152
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:53,000
(Yu Masuda) You can pass by No. 2. (Teruhiko Nemoto) I'll carry the ransom.

153
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
nice!

154
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,000
Mr. Masuda...! I'm going!

155
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
(Swan) I asked for it! yes!

156
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:07,000
♬〜

157
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
(Sound of fastening seatbelt) Please!

158
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:30,000
♬〜

159
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,000
Stop the truck!

160
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,000
