164
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,000
learn!

165
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:51,000
Use the emergency stairs to get to the roof.

166
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,000
Let's go!

167
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:00,000
The truck isn't bad either.

168
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:04,000
We might be the second star. The second one is unbearable...

169
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:08,000
If so, transfer to the Mobile Investigation Division.

170
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,000
No more!

171
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:24,000
♬〜

172
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,000
We arrived at the rooftop!

173
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:35,000
(breathing heavily)

174
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
No one!

175
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,000
Wait there.

176
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:55,000
♬〜

177
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:01,000
